## Section 3

A code block that would otherwise push things off screen:

```js
function fibonacci(n) {
  if (n <= 1) return n
  return fibonacci(n - 1) + fibonacci(n - 2)
}

for (let i = 0; i < 10; i++) {
  console.log(fibonacci(i))
}
```

